org.apache.archiva.common

Class Try<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.archiva.common.Try<V>

  • public abstract class Try<V>
extends Object
    This is a class that can be used for the Try monad The Try monad is able to collect exceptions during processing of a stream.
